trans-unit.source: The NamedImagesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects, which are objects that have an associated image and a name that is unique to the collection.
trans-unit.target: NamedImagesCollection 클래스의 컬렉션을 나타냅니다 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>개체는 연결 된 이미지 및 컬렉션에 고유한 이름을 가진 개체입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This class is exposed as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property of the root <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object, and is only available at run time.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는으로 노출 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>루트의 컬렉션 속성 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>개체와 사용할 수 런타임에.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>

trans-unit.source: An image can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image> class, such as <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, which is created dynamically.
trans-unit.target: 이미지에는.NET Framework에서 파생 된 개체 수 <xref:System.Drawing.Image>클래스 같은 <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>를 동적으로 생성 됩니다.</xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> </xref:System.Drawing.Image>

trans-unit.source: The image can be stored in this collection, and then assigned at a later time to any image property in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control, such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 이미지를이 컬렉션에 저장 하 고 나중 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A> 등의 컨트롤</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> 에서 이미지 속성에 할당 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property, of type NamedImagesCollection, is first checked to see if an image with that name exists.
trans-unit.target: 때에서 이미지 속성 중 하나는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>컨트롤을 지정 하 여 설정는 `string` 값의 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>NamedImagesCollection, 형식의 컬렉션 속성을 해당 이름의 이미지 있는지을 먼저 확인 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: 일치 하는 경우 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>개체를 찾았지만,이 이미지 사용 됩니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is not located, the string expression is treated as a URL, image resource name or pathname.
trans-unit.target: 일치 하는 경우 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>개체 위치한, 문자열 식이 URL, 이미지 리소스 이름 또는 경로 이름으로 처리 됩니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>
